SELECT COALESCE("Users"."Id", "Users"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", CASE WHEN "t1"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t1"."GOLDCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."GOLDCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t1"."SILVERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."SILVERCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t1"."BRONZECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."BRONZECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTALPOSTS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTALPOSTS" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALPOSTS", CASE WHEN "t3"."QUESTIONCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."QUESTIONCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."ANSWERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."ANSWERCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTALSCORE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTALSCORE" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALSCORE"
FROM "STACK"."Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT ANY_VALUE("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZECOUNT"
FROM "STACK"."Badges"
RIGHT JOIN "STACK"."Users" AS "Users0" ON "Badges"."UserId" = "Users0"."Id"
GROUP BY "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."DisplayName") AS "t1" ON "Users"."Id" = "t1"."USERID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "OwnerUserId" AS "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALPOSTS", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "ANSWERCOUNT", SUM("Score") AS "TOTALSCORE"
FROM "STACK"."Posts"
GROUP BY "OwnerUserId") AS "t3" ON "Users"."Id" = "t3"."OWNERUSERID"
WHERE CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTALPOSTS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTALPOSTS" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END > 0